Regular secondary structures were identified using the well-established empirical relationships with 13C chemical shifts (Saito 1986; Pastore and Saudek 1990; Spera and Bax 1991; Wishart and Sykes 1994; Luginbühl et al. 1995). The Fig. 2 shows a plot of the deviations of the experimentally observed 13C chemical shifts from the random coil values, Δδi, versus the amino acid sequence, where Δδi is defined as \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
